* PERL 5.12 PKGBUILD

Here is a repo to generate, and hopefully later, test the perl 5.12
package for Archlinux.

Right now there is not much to it.  Just run "make.pl" to
generate a PKGBUILD.

** WARNING

Perl512Provides.pm is not perfect.  Right now we lookup modules on
CPAN, using CPANPLUS.  However, this is looking up the latest module
versions.  I haven't yet figured out how to only lookup the module
versions specified by Module::CoreList.

** TODO
